ic 'restricted movement' to 780 million people}}</ref>\n<ref name=\"AutoDW-9\">{{cite web |url=https://knpr.org/npr/2020-01/coronavirus-update-masks-and-temperature-checks-hong-kong |title=Coronavirus Update: Masks And Temperature Checks In Hong Kong |work=Nevada Public Radio |access-date=26 January 2020}}</ref>\n<ref name=\"CDC Travel\">{{cite web |url=https://www.cdc.gov/coronavirus/2019-ncov/travelers/index.html |title=Coronavirus Disease 2019 Information for Travel |date=3 February 2020 |work=US [[Centers for Disease Control and Prevention]] (CDC) |url-status=live |archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20200130163513/https://www.cdc.gov/coronavirus/2019-ncov/travelers/index.html |archive-date=30 January 2020 |access-date=6 February 2020}}</ref>\n<ref name=\"Level4\">{{cite news |url=https://www.usatoday.com/story/travel/news/2020/01/24/coronavirus-outbreak-leads-state-department-issue-level-4-advisory/4562349002/ |title=Coronavirus: US says 'do not travel' to Wuhan, China, as airlines issue waivers, add safeguards |last=Deerwester |first=Jayme |last2=Gilbertson |first2=Dawn |work=[[USA Today]] |url-status=live |archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20200127063342/https://www.usatoday.com/story/travel/news/2020/01/24/coronavirus-outbreak-leads-state-department-issue-level-4-advisory/4562349002/ |archive-date=27 January 2020 |access-date=26 January 2020}}</ref>\n<ref name=\"AutoDW-10\">{{cite web |url=https://www.gov.uk/guidance/wuhan-novel-coronavirus-information-for-the-public#advice-for-travellers |title=Coronavirus (COVID-19): latest information and advice |publisher=Government of the United Kingdom |access-date=27 February 2020}}</ref>\n<ref name=\"EUPrepares\">{{cite news |title=Coronavirus Live Updates: Europe Prepares for Pandemic as Illness Spreads From Italy |url=https://www.nytimes.com/2020/02/26/world/asia/coronavirus-news.html |work=[[The New York Times]] |access-date=26 February 2020 |date=26 February 2020}}</ref>\n<ref name=\"Huang24Jan2020\">